Text: What happen to them? anybody knows? are they coming back?

Hey, I am interested to know too what happened to them. Been waiting for the August publication as KCN does not have 100% same serials as serial box has. Also I like the iSerial reader much more as it is easy to show only those serials that are new in month. Thanks for all those who have been supply here Serial Box and KCN releases.
If you read on the front page of iSerial once you install the 7-2009 Serial Box, it tells you that they will be not be making an August collection, but will return in September with one.

On the last Serial Box (07) there is a text:

No isue in august.
Next isue: 09.2009

EyeOfBeauty
Where is the Serial Box 08.2009 - August??
I be damned! You are right, opened my iSerial reader and it does indeed say that Serial Box will resume in August. Awesome. Thanks. :) Most times don't read the fine print. ;)
